===評價===
《天眼行動》獲得了正面好評。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]新鮮度93%<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/eye_in_the_sky/|title=Eye in the Sky (2016)|publisher=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|accessdate=April 3, 2016|archive-date=2016-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160407071216/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/eye_in_the_sky/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]得分73<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/eye-in-the-sky|title=Eye in the Sky|publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=April 5, 2016|archive-date=2016-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160409001152/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/eye-in-the-sky|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

《[[芝加哥太陽報|芝加哥太陽報]]》的專欄影評人{{link-en|李察·洛普|Richard Roeper}}除了給電影好評外，還特別稱讚了艾倫·瑞克曼的優異演出<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://chicago.suntimes.com/columnists/eye-in-the-sky-helen-mirren-co-stars-excel-in-tense-war-drama/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2016-04-06 |archive-date=2016-03-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160321071806/http://chicago.suntimes.com/columnists/eye-in-the-sky-helen-mirren-co-stars-excel-in-tense-war-drama/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

